!!!Creating a New Wiki Page
1. On the left bar, go to Wiki > Create a Wiki Page. 
2. Enter appropriate information.
3. Go to the Categories tab and list it under whatever applies. This will greatly improve searching functions, especially for later years.
4. Click save.

!!!Searching for Wiki Pages


!!!Editing Wiki Pages


!!!Adding Users
1. Go to the Users button in the top right of the page (if you have the permissions to do so). It looks like a person.
2. Go to the ===Add New User=== tab and enter appropriate information.
3. Uncheck the box next to ===Send an email to the user in order to allow him to validate his account.===